    <!-- Project Summary Section -->
    <p>Project Summary: This web application allows users to manage stock portfolios, view real-time stock prices, and perform CRUD operations to track their investments. The stock data is fetched from an external API and stored in an in-memory database for real-time tracking and analysis.</p>

    <!-- GitHub Repository Link -->
